DOC.brief_summary: The purpose of this study is to determine whether HIV patients on Atazanavir who have Hyperbilirubinemia have different outcomes from those without Hyperbilirubinemia.
DOC.brief_title: Impact of Hyperbilirubinemia Among HIV Patients Treated With Atazanavir
DOC.criteria: Diagnosis of Human immunodeficiency virus Treatment with Atazanavir 18 yrs and older
